MESSAGE.DESCRIPTION: Are you trying to navigate within the app?

NAV_BUTTONS.DESCRIPTION: You can use the < and > navigation buttons to return to a previous Concept or Panel.
NAV_BUTTONS.CONCEPTS: Concept buttons are on the far right of the Concept selection control.
NAV_BUTTONS.PANELS: Panel buttons are on the far left of the top navigation bar.
NAV_BUTTONS.LONG_PRESS: You can long press the nav buttons to jump to a specific point in their history as well.

MESSAGE.BROWSER_BACK: The browser back button closes the Knowledge Base app and logs you out.
MESSAGE.CONFIRM: Are you sure you want to logout?
